<lyrics>[V1]
 1- kil̊maẗu ạllhi gẖadā
 jasadaⁿạ yā lal̊ʿajab̊
 wafadānā kulãnā
 sẖāribaⁿạ kā̊̉sa ạl̊gẖaḍab̊

[V2]
 2- ʿajabaⁿạ min̊ ḥubĩ man̊
 nāba ʿanãạ biạlrĩḍay̱
 falidẖā māta waqad̊
 qāma ạảẙḍaⁿạ wār̊taqay̱

[V3]
 3- mut̊nā ạảẙḍaⁿạ maʿahu
 wāảqāmanā maʿaⁿạ
 wafīhi ạảj̊lasanā
 wamaqāmunā samā

[V4]
 4- fāf̊raḥūạ yā man̊ bihi
 ḥuz̊tumu ạl̊ḥubã ạl̊ʿajīb̊
 wāsẖ̊kurūạ ạlậba ʿalay̱
 dẖā ạl̊maqāmi fī ạl̊ḥabīb̊</lyrics>
<title>klmẗ ạllh gẖdạ</title>
</song>